  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.2.0-beta01\" data-text=\"Version 1.2.0-beta01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.2.0-beta01</h3>\n<p>May 11, 2022</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.compose.material:material-*:1.2.0-beta01</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/41a4e31408842caa2b58db5e4ee6ec708464425f..eea19c54f6d94f1c234c4305c1329f7f1427867a/compose/material\">Version 1.2.0-beta01 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>New Features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>This is the first beta release of 1.2!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>API Changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Renamed <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">TextFieldDefaults.BorderStroke</code> composable that draws a border stroke in <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">OutlinedTextField</code> to <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">TextFieldDefaults.BorderBox</code>. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I5f295062ff2a3ebc72115df2412062558d226273\">I5f295</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
